"All our remaining matches are ones we can really challenge for."
Ballinamallard will be without the suspended Ryan McConnell but Stuart Hutchinson is set to return.
"It will be a massive challenge as they are fighting for their lives - it's going be a tough game," said Mallards manager Gavin Dykes.
